// Trauma


Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Shoulder MRI

When I select 'Luxation' checkbox
Then '1X' radio button is enabled
And 'More than 1x' radio button is enabled
And 'Ventral' radio button is enabled
And 'Ventral subluxation' radio button is enabled
And 'Dorsal' radio button is enabled
And 'Dorsal subluxation' radio button is enabled
And 'Spontaneous reduction' radio button is enabled
And 'Non-surgical reduction' radio button is enabled
And 'Month' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Year' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Fracture' checkbox
Then 'Humeral head' checkbox is enabled
And 'Scapula' checkbox is enabled
And 'Glenoid' checkbox is enabled
And 'Clavicle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Month' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Year' dropdown menu is enabled
